textAnnotations.description:
Note to be attached to Plan No. 56 (Proposed deviation
of Kampala-Toro Road to Mubende)
It will be noticed that the position of the junction of
the road to Mahende on this plan does not agree with that on
No. 55.
This difference is due to an error in the traverse
of 12 chains which was corrected so as to close on the I. P.
lubende (2)".
It is possible that the error may be found on checking
the computations which owing to pressure of work has up to the
present been impossible.
GANDA
PROTECTOR
20 JUL 1903
SURVEY DE
DEPARTHE
WOMAT/AFR/ BEA/189/6/3
